query: SELECT SUM(price) FROM Orders WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2025'
SELECT STRFTIME('%m', date) AS month, SUM(price) FROM Orders WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2025' GROUP BY month
SELECT SUM(price) FROM DeletedOrders WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2025'
SELECT STRFTIME('%m', date) AS month, SUM(price) FROM DeletedOrders WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', date) = '2025' GROUP BY month
SELECT T2.uname, SUM(T1.price) FROM Orders AS T1 INNER JOIN User AS T2 ON T1.cashier = T2.userid WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', T1.date) = '2025' GROUP BY T2.uname
SELECT T2.uname, SUM(T1.price) FROM DeletedOrders AS T1 INNER JOIN User AS T2 ON T1.cashier = T2.userid WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', T1.date) = '2025' GROUP BY T2.uname
SELECT SUM(T1.price) FROM Orders AS T1 INNER JOIN DiscountedOrders AS T2 ON T1.billno = T2.billno  WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', T1.date) = '2025'
SELECT SUM(T1.price) FROM Orders AS T1 WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', T1.date) = '2025' AND T1.billno NOT IN (SELECT billno FROM DiscountedOrders)
